From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


This is a maintenance category, used for maintenance of the Wikipedia project. It is not part of the encyclopedia and contains non-article pages, or groups articles by status rather than subject. Do not include this category in content categories.This is a container category. Due to its scope, it should only contain subcategories.ShortcutCAT:CATCAT:CAT



Wikimedia Commons has media related to Categories.

Not to be confused with Category:Wikipedia or Category:Categories in category theory.
For the overall top-level category, see Category:Contents.
This category is for types of categories and subcategories of pages about Wikipedia categories.
